description: Lofted 1 bedroom 1 bathroom condo on Telegraph Hill in South Boston! This unit features washer and dryer in unit, new kitchen, and private back deck with roof rights. It was thoughtfully renovated to maximize space without compromising style. Brand new stairs with built in storage were built to access the lofted bedroom. The renovated kitchen includes white shaker cabinets, quartz counters and a large peninsula for communal meals overlooking the living room. With a quintessential bay window in the front and an oversized skylight, the space is sunny and welcoming. Dine al fresco on your back deck off the kitchen while you dream of the amazing views you will have when you build your roof deck! Known as the San Francisco of Boston, Telegraph Hill is filled with beautiful Victorian row houses, and is an ideal location right near the East and West Broadway split so you don't have to choose between the west and east side, instead you are close to all- including the beach!
